   Love came the second time around for former
baseball star Steve Garvey and his new wife, and he was so sure he
rushed their wedding ahead by four months.
   ``I just couldn't live without her and I had to have her down
here,'' Garvey said Wednesday of Candace Thomas, 30.
   The two were married Saturday in her parents' home in Deer
Valley, a ski resort near Park City, Utah, before 10 friends and
