<HEAD>Councilman Swings At Attorney During Council Meeting</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DALLAS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A city councilman leaped from his seat during a
meeting and engaged in a scuffle with an attorney who he said called
him ``yellow and a coward.''
   Councilman Al Gonzalez marched into the gallery during
Wednesday's meeting, stunning Mayor Annette Strauss and the rest of
