<TEXT>
   Former U.S. Attorney Rudolph Giuliani registered
a political committee Thursday with the city Board of Elections,
clearing the way for fund-raising for a possible run for mayor.
   Dennison Young Jr., an aide, announced the filing, which he said
does not commit Giuliani to running.
   Giuiliani, who stepped down as U.S. attorney last month and
