<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY44</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Bridget loves Bernie no more. ``Family Ties''
actress Meredith Baxter Birney and actor David Birney say they are
