Uruguay, Peru, Ecuador, Nicaragua, Cuba and Haiti.
   In Uruguay, Mrs. Mitterrand will preside over a French film
festival and in Peru she will inaugurate a children's home.
   Mrs. Mitterrand will meet with leaders from several
non-governmental humanitarian organizations in Nigaragua before
traveling to Cuba for a meeting with President Fidel Castro. She
will return to Paris from Haiti on March 12.
