<HEAD>Crop Futures Finish Narrowly Mixed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Wheat and soybean futures prices closed narrowly
mixed while other grain futures finished lower Thursday in a quiet
session on the Chicago Board of Trade.
